sub_title: Founder SUE Behavioural Design, Behavioural Design Academy, co-founder SUE & The Alchemists | Keynote speaker | Psychologist | TedX speaker | Columnist
summary: Co-Founder of SUE | Behavioural Design And SUE & The Alchemists. We're a team of psychologists and creatives that turn deep insights on customer behaviour into marketing communication strategies that actually work. SUE is working before and behind the screen across industries like media, politics, finance, B2B and social profit. Our mission is to nudge people into positive choices. Our culture can be best described as Knalldrang.
